2019t power off the device remotely, but you can disable many of its functions:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open the <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Google_Home\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Home<\/a> app<\/li>\n<li>Tap on your device<\/li>\n<li>Access settings to mute volume or restrict voice commands<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>\u00a0Alternative: Unplug the Device<\/h2>\n<p>If you want to stop all functions, unplugging it is the most direct method. Once powered off, it won\u2019t respond to any commands or background processes.<\/p>\n<h2>\u00a0Does It Affect Performance?<\/h2>\n<p>Frequent unplugging won\u2019t damage the speaker, but it will reset ongoing sessions and possibly require reinitialization of certain settings.<\/p>\n<h2>\u00a0Final Advice<\/h2>\n<p>Whether you're aiming for privacy or energy saving, turning off your Google Home Mini speaker is doable. For complete shutdown, unplug the device. For limited control, toggle the mic or manage via the app.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>How to Turn Off Google Home Mini Speaker Trying to figure out how to turn off your Google Home Mini speaker? While the device is designed to stay on 24\/7, there are several ways to disable its functionality temporarily or completely. Here\u2019s a simple breakdown. \u00a0Can You Fully Turn It Off? The Google Home Mini &#8230; <a title=\"How to turn off google home mini speaker?\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/idt.ydns.eu\/how-to-turn-off-google-home-mini-speaker\/\" aria-label=\"Read more about How to turn off google home mini speaker?\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-248","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-google-home-mini-speaker"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site 